content: You can't move the folder to its subfolder

comment.text: This translation key is used for displaying an error message when attempting to move a folder into its own subfolder in the FilesSelector component. The message appears as an alert after selecting a file or folder.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Qovluğu alt qovluğuna köçürə bilməzsiniz' is a literal translation and while understandable, it's not the most natural way to express this in Azerbaijani. A more natural phrasing would focus on the restriction.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Qovluğu öz alt qovluğuna daşımağa icazə yoxdur.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Ordner können nicht in Unterordner verschoben werden' is a literal translation but sounds unnatural in German. A more idiomatic translation would be 'You cannot move a folder into a subfolder' or 'Folders cannot be moved into subfolders'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Ordner können nicht in einen Unterordner verschoben werden.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Armenian translation 'Դուք չեք կարող պանակը տեղափոխել իր ենթաթղթապանակ' is a literal translation but sounds unnatural in Armenian. A more natural phrasing would be 'You cannot move a folder into one of its subfolders'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Ադրբէջանական Կրտսերգը չի կարող պանակը տեղափոխել իր ենթաթղթապանակի մեջ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'බහාලුමක් එහි උප බහාලුමකට ගෙන යාමට නොහැකිය' is a literal translation but doesn't quite convey the natural flow of the English phrase 'You can't move the folder to its subfolder'. It sounds a bit awkward in Sinhala.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider a more natural phrasing like: 'බහාලුම එහි උප බහාලුමට මාරුවාගත නොහැක' or 'බහාලුම එහි උප-බහාලුමට නොකියවනු ලැබේ'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Serbian translation 'Не можете померити фолдер у његов подфолдер' is not an accurate translation of 'You can't move the folder to its subfolder'. The verb 'померити' (pomеriti) means 'to move' but in this context, 'преместити' (premeštiti) would be more appropriate, emphasizing the relocation.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Не можете преместити фолдер у његов подфолдер
